text: "I'll Supply the Love" is a 1979 song by American rock band Toto. It is the second single from their debut studio album Toto. It went to number 45 in the United States, number 73 in Canada, number 92 in Australia and number 29 in New Zealand. == References == Category:1979 songs Category:Toto (band) songs Category:Hard rock songs Category:Funk rock songs
title: I'll Supply the Love
